#### Personal Training Service
* This is for Personal Trainers and similar professionals.
* It allows them to offer their services online, and make money when training clients who are remote.
* It allows them to record and offer videos.
* Includes a way to send text message reminders and motivators to clients.
* Allows them to live stream (two way) for individual or pair classes.
